Interface ReentrantPanel

All Known Implementing Classes:
AdvancedOptionsPanel, BasicInformationPanel, EntityDetailsPanel, ExtensionTablePanel, ExtensionTlTablePanel, FlexfieldPanel, ParametersBasePanel, ParametersPanel, ParametersPanel, PrimaryTablePanel, PrimaryTablePanel, SecondaryTablesPanel, SummaryPanel, SummaryPanel
public interface ReentrantPanel

Interface used to determine mark panels that need to have a enter method called on navigation to the panel. This enter method can be used to populate the panel from the wizard model.
